dct_title_s: Map of the common lands from 26th Street to 43rd Street : showing the old streets and plots as surveyed and mapped in 1796 by Cassimer T.H. Goerck, City Surveyor, and the distance between those old streets and our present streets
dct_description_sm: Cadastral map. Includes names of some modern land owners. Oriented with north to the upper left. Hand colored. Includes text.
